/*                                                               *
/* Wiring Instruction:                                           *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 1  (TX)   -> Pin D1 / GPIO5                 *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 2  (RX)   -> Pin D2 / GPIO4                 *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 3  (GND)  -> GND                            *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 4  (2.5m) -> unused                         *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 5  (5V)   -> VU                             *
/*      - SDS011 Pin 6  (1m)   -> unused                         *
/*                                                               *
